      • recoverFills

        protected void recoverFills(ObjectInput in)
                     throws IOException,
                            ClassNotFoundException
        Recover the order's fill data from the input stream.

        On successful completion the fills member is set to the recovered fills.

        Parameters:
        in - The input stream.
        Throws:
        IOException - On error reading from the output stream.
        ClassNotFoundException - If a fill of an unrecognized type is encountered in the input stream. This should never happen.
